title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1993-09-29
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, The Same Thing, Loose Lucy, Black Throated Wind, Dire Wolf, Eternity, Tennessee Jed

Set 2

Eyes Of The World, Looks Like Rain, Way To Go Home, Terrapin Station-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> Playin' In The Band Reprise, Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Liberty
